room_title: Escape room "Jack the Ripper" by Challenge Accepted in Chicago
room_description: The year is 1888… You find yourself trapped in alley in London. Jack the Ripper has grown tired of his usual victims and has chosen to play a game with you and your friends. If you can find his favorite knife before time runs out… He will let you live! If not… He will have his fun!!!! You only have 20 minutes, your lives are on the line… HURRY!!!!
